snippet.title: Cloud Cutter Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Get ready for classic Arcade SHOOT ‘EM UP gameplay in Top Notch Graphics.
AVAILABLE ON STEAM! https://store.steampowered.com/app/1584750/Cloud_Cutter/

Enjoy intense fast-paced explosive action full of epic destruction, arcade style power-ups, lasers and of course huge multi-stage boss fights.

AVAILABLE  ON STEAM!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1584750/Cloud_Cutter/
